name: Egg x-ray
description:
This will produce x-rays of bellies filled with eggs. Both good at generating and inpainting

Use prompt xray_eggs to activate it

Generates the best results with:

large white xray_eggs inside pregnant belly

where white and large can be varied

This dataset is trained on a select few images. If you generate good results, put them in the comments, and I will train a V2 with them
